4Ô∏è‚É£ Update hotelservice.ts

deleteHotel(id: number, token: string): Observable<any> {
  const headers = new HttpHeaders({ Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` });
  return this.http.delete(`${this.apiUrl}/${id}`, { headers, responseType: 'text' });
}

> ‡§π‡•á ‡§Æ‡§π‡§§‡•ç‡§§‡•ç‡§µ‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á ‡§ï‡§æ‡§∞‡§£ backend plain text return ‡§ï‡§∞‡§§‡•ã ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø Angular default JSON parsing ok: false error ‡§¶‡•á‡§§‡•á.




